#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:57
msgid ""
"The /rules endpoint allows for retrieving the raw unprocessed source (the "
"whole ruleset, not transformed into a CPRMV ruleset if the source isn’t a "
"CPRMV ruleset)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:58
msgid ""
"The /rules endpoint adds :publication-location property to RuleSet’s with an "
"URI’s as value (This will be the link to repository.overheid.nl in case for "
"BWB,CVDR, an ELI reference in case of Formex 4 (these are seen as root "
"sources for now). In the case of DMN it is the URI to the Operaton server"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:59
msgid ""
"Fix escaping of quotes and newlines in transformations to RDF, which up "
"until 0.4.1 can cause some sources to fail to load"
msgstr ""

