msgid ""
"Improved and more complete support for BWB, CVDR, Formex 4 and DMN 1.3 "
"standards through usage of the existing XML Schema’s independent from XSL "
"stylesheets (CPRMV uses a generic single stylesheet for all XML based "
"standards which are constrained through schema checking)"
msgstr ""

