"start processes related to the resources (as defined by services)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:78
msgid ""
"Adds user friendly access to method knowledge in the /browser section "
"relating to defined services for governance on value lists"
msgstr ""

